@startuml
!include ../include/diagram-style.puml

title Edit Existing Trail Information

actor "End User" as EU
boundary SearchPanel
boundary TrailPanel
control TrailService
database Database

EU -> SearchPanel : search / select trail
EU -> TrailPanel : open trail (from Search or list)

TrailPanel -> TrailService : getTrail(trailId)
TrailService -> Database : fetchTrailById(trailId)
Database --> TrailService : trail
TrailService --> TrailPanel : trail

TrailPanel --> EU : display trail + wildlife + images

EU -> TrailPanel : click "Edit", change name/length/elevation
TrailPanel -> TrailService : editTrail(name, trailId, length, elevation)

TrailService -> TrailService : update Trail fields
TrailService -> Database : save()

Database --> TrailService : ok
TrailService --> TrailPanel : ok

TrailPanel --> EU : refreshed trail fields

@enduml
